  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/2affd40a70f67ba906de4ea5907ec80c.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/bbda813ad61dd3d93de817afed3e03bd.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/bbda813ad61dd3d93de817afed3e03bd.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/bbda813ad61dd3d93de817afed3e03bd.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Party Bots supports up to 100 players in each lobby! Although, the use of powerful gaming computers is recommended in this case! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/ec927ebaf05b547ad4b0c12161a4ffa4.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/a35f3690ca88182323f66b176314b699.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/a35f3690ca88182323f66b176314b699.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/a35f3690ca88182323f66b176314b699.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You start as a regular Y-Bot, but you don't have to look like everyone else! Customize your face, color, and hat to your heart's content!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/29bf414a131cd833e82b6b74c74f44da.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/12afa160e9d4f53bae6a9e20a26dd62d.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/12afa160e9d4f53bae6a9e20a26dd62d.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/12afa160e9d4f53bae6a9e20a26dd62d.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explosions and lasers can destroy platforms in a dynamic and fun way! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/1fc562cd225237b7fa597373c6852de3.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/70aa6344780172c4d49234b71eeae515.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/70aa6344780172c4d49234b71eeae515.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/70aa6344780172c4d49234b71eeae515.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Party Bots is full of new items to unlock. Are you lucky enough to get a really rare one?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/c21745da221c25fa555395c03fdf7bb1.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/54f8a44abf3f259962e787a506aa31f9.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/54f8a44abf3f259962e787a506aa31f9.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/54f8a44abf3f259962e787a506aa31f9.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You can take control of game modes yourself and change everything to your liking! Don't like the explosive barrels? Remove them! Want things to happen faster? Speed up the events! Is the game too easy for you? Make it harder!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/7edeb92dcbd5147c791fd08c06eac3c8.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/3c6aab2b5e4474728152095b37250ba5.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/3c6aab2b5e4474728152095b37250ba5.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/3c6aab2b5e4474728152095b37250ba5.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>This can save you in the most dangerous situations, or just be fun!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/2affd40a70f67ba906de4ea5907ec80c.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/bbda813ad61dd3d93de817afed3e03bd.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/bbda813ad61dd3d93de817afed3e03bd.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/bbda813ad61dd3d93de817afed3e03bd.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Party Bots supports up to 100 players in each lobby! Although, the use of powerful gaming computers is recommended in this case! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/ec927ebaf05b547ad4b0c12161a4ffa4.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/a35f3690ca88182323f66b176314b699.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/a35f3690ca88182323f66b176314b699.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/a35f3690ca88182323f66b176314b699.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You start as a regular Y-Bot, but you don't have to look like everyone else! Customize your face, color, and hat to your heart's content!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/29bf414a131cd833e82b6b74c74f44da.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/12afa160e9d4f53bae6a9e20a26dd62d.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/12afa160e9d4f53bae6a9e20a26dd62d.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/12afa160e9d4f53bae6a9e20a26dd62d.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explosions and lasers can destroy platforms in a dynamic and fun way! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/1fc562cd225237b7fa597373c6852de3.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/70aa6344780172c4d49234b71eeae515.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/70aa6344780172c4d49234b71eeae515.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/70aa6344780172c4d49234b71eeae515.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Party Bots is full of new items to unlock. Are you lucky enough to get a really rare one?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/c21745da221c25fa555395c03fdf7bb1.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/54f8a44abf3f259962e787a506aa31f9.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/54f8a44abf3f259962e787a506aa31f9.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/54f8a44abf3f259962e787a506aa31f9.mp4?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You can take control of game modes yourself and change everything to your liking! Don't like the explosive barrels? Remove them! Want things to happen faster? Speed up the events! Is the game too easy for you? Make it harder!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/7edeb92dcbd5147c791fd08c06eac3c8.webp?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/3c6aab2b5e4474728152095b37250ba5.poster.avif?t=1741311128\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/3c6aab2b5e4474728152095b37250ba5.webm?t=1741311128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859860/extras/3c6aab2b5e4474728152095b37250ba5.mp4?t=1741311128